stanford institute of design d school emerging projects d school at any one moment there are hundreds of projects underway at the d school they range from impromptu challenges that last just an hour or two to 10 week class projects to student teams that continue on to deploy their solutions and start companies when we see strong ongoing student interest in a particular area an initiative forms to support those projects for example an ongoing interest in bringing design thinking to schools and children developed into our k 12 lab our social entrepreneurship lab fosters the extraordinary student interest in using design thinking to create companies that can do good in the world as our students develop interests in new directions d school initiatives will continue to form and develop around them
